Experience the vibrant BMW in Miami with this Chrome extension, blending tropical energy with automotive style in every new tab!

The BMW in Miami live wallpaper extension showcases a stunning view of a BMW set against Miami’s iconic, sun-drenched backdrop. This colorful theme transforms your browsing experience, pairing style with practical features for seamless navigation.

Search the web effortlessly with a Google search bar, access top sites with customizable shortcuts, and stay organized with a clock-date display.

Live Wallpaper featuring a BMW in Miami's vibrant setting
Google Search Bar for easy browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for quick access
Clock-Date display for real-time organization
